description         Command-line interface for the Databricks platform

long_description    The Databricks CLI is an open source tool which provides \
                    an easy-to-use interface to the Databricks platform. It is \
                    built on top of the Databricks REST APIs and includes \
                    support for Databricks Asset Bundles (DABs) for managing \
                    and deploying data and AI projects.

homepage            https://docs.databricks.com/dev-tools/cli/index.html

